    The class Rotaded Icon. Code taken from: https://tips4java.wordpress.com/2009/04/06/rotated-icon/ The RotatedIcon allows you to change the orientation of an Icon by rotating the Icon before it is painted. This class supports the following orientations:
    • DOWN - rotated 90 degrees
    • UP (default) - rotated -90 degrees
    • UPSIDE_DOWN - rotated 180 degrees
    • ABOUT_CENTER - the icon is rotated by the specified degrees about its center.
